being single doesn’t mean your lonely or incomplete. 

you have the freedom to truly focus on yourself, see what makes you happy, what your passions are. you’re learning about yourself, falling in love with yourself, becoming the best version of yourself. this is where you’ll see personal growth. turn every moment into a positive one & find joy in it. 

so bestie, switch that mindset to okay this is my time. enjoy your own company & embrace it because one day you’ll miss this. 

my future husband must be working on himself too so we can be together 😂 but also the dating scene is a joke iykyk.
